# Real-run output dirs are audit artifacts. Ignore historical/unselected run dirs so they
# do not clutter `git status`. The two committed evidence runs are already tracked (these
# negations keep their intent explicit; ignore rules never untrack already-tracked files):
#   results/real_run_20260602_2227_full10/  (primary, full 10/side)
#   results/real_run_20260602_2203/          (secondary, 2-turn quick demo)
results/real_run_*/
!results/real_run_20260602_2203/
!results/real_run_20260602_2227_full10/
